

1. LS          -    This command will help list all the files and folders.

2. Tuoch       -    This is use to create a file

3. Mkdir       -    This command is use to create a folder

4. Ls -al      -    This command is use to list all files and folders including hidden file in a long format

5. cp          -    This is use to copy a file or folder

6. mv          -    It is use to move a folder or file.

7. rm          -    It is use to delete a file

8. rm -f       -    This is to forcefully remove a folder with contents

9. Cat         -    This command is use to see the contents of a file

10. pwd        -    This command will show you your present directory.
